news.title: Chhapra: 184 beneficiaries receive new homes under PMAY
news.para: ​​​​Saran DPRO Ravindra Kumar said that the beneficiaries were given Rs 2.5 lakh in three instalments for construction of their houses as per govt specifications between Oct 24, 2024, and March 25.

news.title: Property prices in Greater Noida surge by 98% in five years
news.para: Over the last decade, NCR has seen a massive resurgence in demand and supply across real estate segments, and key hotspots have witnessed remarkable housing price appreciation.

news.title: US-based AML leases 1.57 lakh sq ft for GCC in Noida
news.para: AML RightSource is among a slew of corporates leasing fresh office space in Noida, enthused by the scheduled opening of the new Jewar airport this year.

news.title: ACC's profit declines 20.4% to Rs 751.04 crore in Q4 FY25
news.para: Its revenue from operations was at Rs 5,207.3 crore, up 12.7 per cent in the March quarter. It was at Rs 5,316.75 crore in the corresponding period a year ago.

news.title: Sales of new homes in USA rise 7.4% in March 2025
news.para: New home sales jumped 7.4% to a seasonally adjusted annual rate of 724,000 units last month, the highest level since September 2024, the Commerce Department's Census Bureau said on Wednesday.

news.title: GCDA to complete construction of shopping complex in Kakkanad soon
news.para: The building will span 18,000 sq ft over five floors, including a basement. Basement will be entirely dedicated to parking, with separate entry and exit routes.

news.title: Construction & demolition waste processing plant in Ludhiana to be operational soon
news.para: Pegged at ₹2.69 crore for the structural work originally, the cost ballooned to ₹7.5 crore after it was discovered the selected site was a former dumpsite.

news.title: New Jersey sues RealPage, top landlords of conspiring to drive up residential rents
news.para: The state said the collusion has inflated rents for hundreds of thousands of residents, with half of low-income renters paying more than 30% of their gross incomes toward rent.

news.title: Maharashtra RERA plans thorough verification of OCs for lapsed projects
news.para: The housing regulator had served notices to the developers of such lapsed projects and has so far received responses from 3,699 project developers stating that the housing project has been completed.

news.title: Vadodara civic body plans to offer rebates on property tax payment by May 23
news.para: VMC started offering rebates to property owners in the city a few years ago. The civic body encourages citizens to pay their taxes without waiting for the bills. Citizens can check their tax on the website of the civic body.

news.title: Kolkata mayor urges KMC to release mutation certificates within 15 days
news.para: According to Hakim, any delay in the issuance of mutation certificates will strengthen a tout raj within the civic corridors.

news.title: Mumbai: MHADA CEO directs departments on timely completion of redevelopment & infrastructure projects
news.para: Redevelopment projects in Abhyudayanagar, Gandhinagar, Aaram Nagar, Patra Chawl, and BDD Chawls, as well as housing projects for police colonies, were discussed.

news.title: Mumbai: BMC directs officials to follow SC guidelines on unauthorised constructions
news.para: The Supreme Court has laid down some guidelines regarding action to evict unauthorised construction. Most of these guidelines are already being followed by the civic body.

news.title: Residents of DLF areas in Gurugram protest against demolition orders
news.para: The CM, who interacted with the protesters and accepted their memorandum, also met with representatives of all five DLF phases at the PWD rest house after the meeting and assured them that their issues would be addressed.

news.title: Max Estates takes over Delhi One project in Noida
news.para: The total sales and annuity rental income potential of Delhi One project is estimated to be over ₹2,000 crore and over ₹120 crore respectively.

news.title: Chandigarh administration reduces property tax hike after outrage
news.para: As per the revised notification, 3 times hike in property tax on residential properties was reduced to two times. In the commercial segment, 6% of the annual rateable value was decreased to 5%.

news.title: Mumbai: ITAT declares Rs 2.6 crore flat received for vacating land as non-taxable
news.para: The first win came when he secured a valuable flat in Orchid Enclave in south Mumbai, through a settlement with the real estate redeveloper.

news.title: Demand for industrial & warehousing space falls 47% in Mumbai & Pune in Q4 FY25: Colliers
news.para: The gross leasing of industrial & warehousing space rose 15 per cent in January-March across top eight cities to 90 lakh sq ft from 78 lakh square feet in the year-ago period.

news.title: Bajaj Housing Finance profit rises 54% to Rs 5.87 billion in Q4 FY25
news.para: The country's biggest home loan financier by market value reported a 54% jump in profit to 5.87 billion rupees ($68.8 million) for the three months ending March 31.

news.title: Pune records 24,430 property registrations in March 2025
news.para: “Pune’s real estate market has demonstrated remarkable growth in March 2025, driven by robust end-user demand, attractive affordability, and a conducive business ecosystem.
